# Expires: Updated regularly
# Last modified: 23 Apr 2023 21:48 UTC
# Version: 2023.0423.2148.55
# Syntax: Mikrotik rsc import file (including possible subdomains)
# Number of entries: 126
#
# for RouterOS 6.x
#
